    "Thus, this approach augments the explainability of the attention mechanism since it relies on the attention weights assigned for each graph instance rather than only weights between inputs and outcomes.",
    "The work in Peng et al. (2021) shows that its model learns interpretable representations according to the structure of an ontology given as input.",
